[SN]TITLE[SN]
Family of missing man Robert Brandon informed of body find

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A body has been found in Gower with the family of a missing man informed, South Wales Police has said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The discovery was made in the Ilston Valley area at about 10:30 GMT on Thursday.
While the body has not yet been formally identified, the family of Robert Brandon from Townhill, Swansea, have been informed.
Mr Brandon has been missing since 31 January.
